# Implementation Plan - Add Timer to Capitalization Game

Add a 1-minute timer for each question in the Capitalization game. When the timer runs out, the current progress is auto-submitted.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The timer will be set to 60 seconds (1 minute) per question. If the user doesn't submit in time, the game will automatically process their current corrections as the final answer for that question.

## Proposed Changes

### [Component: Capitalization Game]

#### [MODIFY] [index.html](file:///d:/CHAD/GRAMMAR%20TREATS%20APRIL%209%20FINALE/Grammar%20Treatsv15.13/games/capitalization/index.html)
